gwt.g3d.resources.client
Annotation Type WrapMode

@Inherited
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface WrapMode

Specifies the texture wrapping mode. If this annotation is marked on a texture resource such as ExternalTexture2DResource, the resource will has its wrap mode sets to the value declared.
